long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A time analysis and management tool that helps you analyze Internet usage and help you regulate your online activities. Includes data visualization options and customization to tailor your own online activities. It also has the option to remind you about potential eye-strains to help you protect your optical health.
